title: Educator.com - Pre-Algebra with Nancy Fung
description:
Having a solid foundation in Pre-Algebra is indispensable for setting up a proper mathematical background to succeed in more advanced math and science. Professor Nancy Fung will give you the tools you need by guiding you through all the topics you will most likely see in school. Topics start from Algebraic Expressions to Equations, Rates and Proportions, Linear Functions and Graphing, Inequalities, and end with Test Taking Strategies.
